31/* this file defines the CHIP_ and family flags used in the pciids,
32 * its is common between kms and non-kms because duplicating it and
33 * changing one place is fail.
34 */

36#define RADEON_FAMILY_H

38 * Radeon chip families

106/*
107 * Chip flags
108 */
109enum radeon_chip_flags {
110 RADEON_FAMILY_MASK = 0x0000ffffUL,
111 RADEON_FLAGS_MASK = 0xffff0000UL,
112 RADEON_IS_MOBILITY = 0x00010000UL,
113 RADEON_IS_IGP = 0x00020000UL,
114 RADEON_SINGLE_CRTC = 0x00040000UL,
115 RADEON_IS_AGP = 0x00080000UL,
116 RADEON_HAS_HIERZ = 0x00100000UL,
117 RADEON_IS_PCIE = 0x00200000UL,
118 RADEON_NEW_MEMMAP = 0x00400000UL,
119 RADEON_IS_PCI = 0x00800000UL,
120 RADEON_IS_IGPGART = 0x01000000UL,
121 RADEON_IS_PX = 0x02000000UL,
122};

124#endif
